  FR-5, "docs/architecture/modules/state-management.md":
    sections[7]{name,content,estimatedLines}:
      "TaskState v4スキーマ", "70フィールド定義: identity(taskId/taskName/version=4) phaseTracking(phase/completedPhases/skippedPhases/subPhaseStatus) sizing(size/riskScore) intent(userIntent/openQuestions/notInScope) scope(scopeFiles/scopeDirs/scopeGlob/plannedFiles) traceability(acceptanceCriteria/rtmEntries/proofLog/invariants) checkpoint paths extended(approvals/feedbackLog/baseline/testResults/resetHistory/testFiles/knownBugs) sprint1-2(retryCount/artifactTimestamps/requirementCount/artifactHashes/parallelPhaseBackupLog) security(sessionToken/stateIntegrity) metadata(createdAt/updatedAt/parentTaskId/childTaskIds)", 35
      "Zodバリデーション", "TaskStateSchema: taskId=z.string().uuid() taskName=z.string().min(1) version=z.literal(4) phase=z.enum(PHASE_NAMES) size=z.enum(['small','medium','large']) userIntent=z.string().min(20) sessionToken=z.string().min(32) passthrough()で未知フィールド許容", 20
      "HMAC-SHA256署名", "algorithm=sha256 keyGeneration=randomBytes(32).toString('hex')=64hex chars keyRotation=current+previous verifyStateWithRotation=2鍵検証 signState=canonical JSON(sorted keys)→HMAC sessionToken=randomBytes(32) taskId=crypto.randomUUID()", 25
      "StateManager 22メソッド", "", 30
      "永続化・読取・書込", "manager-read.ts: loadTaskFromDisk(JSON.parse+HMAC検証)/listTasksFromDisk/buildTaskIndex manager-write.ts: persistState(JSON書出)/createTaskState(初期化+HMAC署名)/signAndPersist/updateCheckpoint/applyAddAC/applyAddRTM/applyUpdateACStatus/applyUpdateRTMStatus/appendProgressLog(claude-progress.txt)", 25
      "Reflector-Curator-ACE 3層パイプライン", "Reflector: stashFailure(失敗時)→promoteStashedFailure(成功時)→getLessonsForPhase(注入)。MAX_LESSONS=50 qualityScore=helpful/(helpful+harmful+1)。Curator: runCuratorCycle(completed時)→stale剪定(30日+hitCount<=1)→fuzzyDedup(similarity>=0.7)→stashedFailures清掃(7日)→trim(MAX=40)。ACE: extractAndStoreBullets(quality>=0.6昇格)→ace-context.json永続化→getTopCrossTaskBullets(タスク横断知識注入)", 35
      "不変条件管理", "Invariant型(id:INV-N/description/status:held|violated|pending/evidence) applyAddInvariant/applyUpdateInvariantStatus/checkInvariantCompleteness(DoDゲートL3)", 25
